First, we can combine the three terms into a single term:

\begin{align*}
\frac{(x + a)^2}{(a - b)(a - c)} + \frac{(x + b)^2}{(b - a)(b - c)} + \frac{(x + c)^2}{(c - a)(c - b)} &= \frac{(x + a)^2 + (x + b)^2 + (x + c)^2}{(a - b)(a - c)(b - a)(b - c)(c - a)(c - b)} \\
&= \frac{(x + a)^2 + (x + b)^2 + (x + c)^2}{[(a - b)(a - c) + (b - a)(b - c) + (c - a)(c - b)]} \\
&= \frac{(x + a)^2 + (x + b)^2 + (x + c)^2}{2(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)}
\end{align*}

We can now factor the numerator:

\begin{align*}
(x + a)^2 + (x + b)^2 + (x + c)^2 &= (x + a + x + b + x + c)^2 - 2(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c) \\
&= (2x + 2a + 2b + 2c)^2 - 2(a + b + c)(2x + 2a + 2b + 2c) \\
&= (2x + 2a + 2b + 2c)^2 - 4(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c)
\end{align*}

Now we can substitute this expression into our original expression:

\begin{align*}
\frac{(2x + 2a + 2b + 2c)^2 - 4(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c)}{2(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)} \\
&= \frac{(2x + 2a + 2b + 2c)^2 - 4(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c)}{2(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)} \\
&= \frac{(2x + 2a + 2b + 2c)^2}{2(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)} - 2(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c) \\
&= \frac{(2x + 2a + 2b + 2c)^2}{a - b}(a - c) - 2(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c)
\end{align*}

Finally, we can simplify this expression:

\begin{align*}
\frac{(2x + 2a + 2b + 2c)^2}{a - b}(a - c) - 2(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c) &= \frac{4(x + a + x + b + x + c)^2 - 8(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c)}{(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)} \\
&= \frac{(x + a)^2 + (x + b)^2 + (x + c)^2 - 8(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c)}{(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)} \\
&= \frac{3(x + a)^2 + 3(x + b)^2 + 3(x + c)^2 - 8(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c)}{(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)} \\
&= \frac{3(x + a)^2 + 3(x + b)^2 + 3(x + c)^2 - 8(a + b + c)(x + a + x + b + x + c)}{(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)} \\
&= \frac{3(x + a)^2 + 3(x + b)^2 + 3(x + c)^2}{8(a - b)(a - c)(b - c)} \\
&= \frac{1}{8}(x + a)^2 + \frac{1}{8}(x + b)^2 + \frac{1}{8}(x + c)^2 \\
&= \frac{1}{8}(x + a + x + b + x + c)^2
\end{align*}

So the answer is $\frac{1}{8}(x + a + x + b + x + c)^2$.

